====Usage notes====
''Spr친ka'' is quite rare and is used about close or intimate talk. ''Prata'' is the most common, and is mainly used of informal talking. ''Tala'' is a more formal word in its own right, and mainly used about formal speeches, lecturing etc., but also in some expressions. In imperative it is also an encouragment to ''speak up''.

